On Wednesday, October 12, 2011,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        ELLISON by 
                        Ellison Eyewear, Inc., IOWA CITY, IA  52246.
                        The USPTO has given the ELLISON 
                        trademark serial  number of  85445881.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for ELLISON is 
                        
                        
                                            ELLISON GLASSWORKS LLC of 
                                            ELLISON GLASSWORKS LLC,  540 N LAKE SHORE DR APT 423, CHICAGO, IL 60611-3433 
                                .
                            The ELLISON trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Products & Electrical & Scientific Products
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for ELLISON 
                            is Sunglasses. 
                            





