Overview






                            Chicago, US                            



 




















            Founders                    







                Admin            



Aristotle Loumis

                                                    CEO & Founder                                                 
Founder of @WearEllison 























                Ellison Eyewear is an socially driven, luxury eyewear brand - the first of its kind, providing lifetime coverage for loss, theft or damage for all purchases with our innovative Club Ellison membership program. We design and manufacturer handmade eyewear and connect customers to a mission. We strive to be successful with three main pillars: We obtain the highest quality materials imported from Italy, lens from Carl Zeiss, all handmade in Greece. With each purchase of our product and membership, Ellison will give sight back to somebody in need. Ellison has attracted A-list advisors and investors, and has been featured in INC, Business Insider, NY Post, Life & Style Magazine, CBS, Fox News, and many more for its novel approach to addressing global problems....
            

                Ellison Eyewear is an socially driven, luxury eyewear brand - the first of its kind, providing lifetime coverage for loss, theft or damage for all purchases with our innovative Club Ellison membership program. We design and manufacturer handmade eyewear and connect customers to a mission. We strive to be successful with three main pillars: We obtain the highest quality materials imported from Italy, lens from Carl Zeiss, all handmade in Greece. With each purchase of our product and membership, Ellison will give sight back to somebody in need. Ellison has attracted A-list advisors and investors, and has been featured in INC, Business Insider, NY Post, Life & Style Magazine, CBS, Fox News, and many more for its novel approach to addressing global problems.            
